# Example VarMap Mapping File - Simplified Format
# This file demonstrates the new simplified mapping format.
# Each identifier appears only once with its first and last usage.
#
# Format: FIRST LAST TYPE CANONICAL NEW
# - FIRST: First occurrence (line:column)
# - LAST: Last occurrence (line:column) 
# - TYPE: func, param, or var
# - CANONICAL: Canonicalized name from VarMap
# - NEW: User-provided replacement name
#
# Example entries:
# FIRST LAST TYPE CANONICAL NEW
1:10 1:10 func fn_7823 addNumbers
1:12 1:25 param param_1 firstNumber
1:14 1:29 param param_2 secondNumber
1:21 1:35 var var_1 sum